When this card is Normal Summoned: You can add 1 "Gagaga" Spell/Trap Card from your Deck to your hand. You can target 1 other "Gagaga" monster you control; the Levels of that monster and this card become the combined current Levels of those 2 monsters, until the end of this turn. You can only use this effect of "Gagaga Sister" once per turn.
